Package: CRSSIO
Title: Package to manage the input/output of CRSS data
Version: 0.5.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Alan", "Butler", , "r.alan.butler+CRSSIO@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to generate input files commmonly used by the
    Colorado River Simulation System (CRSS) from publicly available data, as
    well as functions to modify these files. Figures that are commonly used to
    QA/QC and undersand CRSS results are also automated with this package.
URL: https://github.com/BoulderCodeHub/CRSSIO
BugReports: https://github.com/BoulderCodeHub/CRSSIO/issues
License: CC0
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
